thread.title: BRIEF-Wuxi Best Precision Machinery sees FY 2017 net profit up 15 pct to 20 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Wuxi Best Precision Machinery sees FY 2017 net profit up 15 pct to 20 pct

organizations.name: wuxi best precision machinery co ltd

text:
Jan 19(Reuters) - Wuxi Best Precision Machinery Co Ltd
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 15 percent to 20 percent, or to be 134.5 million yuan to 140.3 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 117 million yuan
* Says increased income from intelligent manufacturing system related business is the main reason for the forecast
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/UFjue1
